<title>UK: English China Clays H1 pretax profits dive.</title>
<headline>English China Clays H1 pretax profits dive.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1996-09-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>Six months ending June 30</p>
<p>			   (million stg unless stated)</p>
<p> Shr (pence)		0.86 loss	    vs 12.27 earnings</p>
<p> Dividend (pence)	 5.5		    vs 5.5</p>
<p> Pretax		     5.7		    vs 55.3</p>
<p> Turnover		   430.4		  vs 454.8</p>
<p>NOTE - The company said it took an 18.6 million stg provision against certain under-performing assets in Continental Europe, the Pacific and Brazil.  </p>
<p> Operating result	 11.6		   vs 58.8</p>
<p> Exceptional		18.6 charge	  vs nil</p>
<p> Interest		   5.9		    vs 5.0</p>
<p> Tax			  8.3		    vs 17.7</p>
<p> Net taxed		  2.6 loss	     vs 37.6 profit</p>
<p> Attributable	     2.7 loss	     vs 37.5 profit</p>
<p>-- London Newsroom +44 171 542 7717</p>
